# NorDug Presentation - Diagrams

## Location

`Presentation-HTML/diagrams/` – Mermaid `.mmd` files and generated `.svg` files.

## Theme

**config.json** defines dark theme with orange accent `#FF6B35`:

```json
{
  "theme": "dark",
  "themeVariables": {
    "primaryColor": "#FF6B35",
    "primaryTextColor": "#ffffff",
    ...
  }
}
```

## Workflow

1. Edit `.mmd` (Mermaid syntax)
2. Export to `.svg` using Mermaid CLI (`mmdc`) or online editor
3. Reference in HTML: `<img src="diagrams/name.svg" alt="...">`

## CLI (if mmdc installed)

```bash
mmdc -i diagram.mmd -o diagram.svg -t config.json
```

